{"allowModDistribution":true,"screenshots":[{"description":"Biome check ensures that structures only generate in the correct biomes. When enabled, generation is skipped if the structure would generate in a biome that does not match its biome rules.","id":1567962,"title":"Generate structures only in specific biomes based on rules","modId":1087551,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1567/962/global_biome_check-webp.webp","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1567/962/310/172/global_biome_check-webp.webp"},{"description":"Flatness check ensures that structures only generate on terrain that is sufficiently flat. When enabled, generation is skipped if the terrain in the area where the structure would generate varies too much in height.","id":1567953,"title":"Generate structures only on flat terrain","modId":1087551,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1567/953/global_flatness_check-webp.webp","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1567/953/310/172/global_flatness_check-webp.webp"},{"description":"Overlap prevention ensures that structures never generate on top of each other. When enabled, generation is skipped if a new structure would overlap with an existing one.","id":1567949,"title":"Prevents structures from overlapping","modId":1087551,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1567/949/overlap_prevention-webp.webp","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1567/949/310/172/overlap_prevention-webp.webp"},{"description":"","id":1567948,"title":"Enable/disable any structure","modId":1087551,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1567/948/disable_all_structures-webp.webp","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1567/948/310/172/disable_all_structures-webp.webp"},{"description":"Structures are organized into categories based on the mods and datapacks in use, making them easier to manage.","id":1567945,"title":"Structure settings","modId":1